---
title: Thai Green Style Double Chicken Curry with Mushrooms and Jasmine Rice
description: Basil, coriander, makrut lime leaves and green chillies give Thai Green its signature colour, as well as its fragrant flavour. Our Thai Green Style Double Chicken Curry only takes 10 minutes to prep for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
